{[(level - 25) / 3] + (level - 27)/4} + [(delay - 34)/3]<br>
<br>
or in your case<br>
<br>
{[(50 - 25) / 3] + [(50 - 27)/4]} + [(51 - 34)/3] = 18<br>
<br>
